comments.body:
I don't think that the `CreateCommand` should be used for `update`; it should be possible to "update" all containers, so we had to look at the container configs and see if we can create/clone another from there.

`CreateCommand` was introduced for `generate systemd` where we needed the exacts arguments on the from the CLI.

@mheon is probably able to give the best estimate what needs to be done to clone.
